'''Strategic materials''' are those materials considered crucial to [[national security]] concerns and [[power projection|military]] applications.<br>

Examples include:
* [[Natural resources]], such as [[Petroleum|Oil]];
* [[Alloy]]s, such as [[steel]], [[aluminum]], and [[titanium]]; and
* [[Composite materials]], such as advanced [[plastic]]s, [[polymer]]s and [[ceramic]]s.
